description: Kendo UI Professional is a complete end-to-end javascript framework for building web and mobile applications with HTML5 and JavaScript. It consists of framework features such as powerful data source for data-binding, blazing fast templates, MVVM, Validation, Globalization, etc. as well as a rich set of widgets for web and mobile development.
